name: .SVS File Extension
type_name: Game Boy Advance Saved State File
summary: Learn about .SVS files and view a list of programs that open them.

description: Contains saved data from an emulated Game Boy Advance (GBA) video game; allows the game to be saved and resumed from the saved state; may be generated by gpSP (game play SP), a GBA emulation program.

content: The gpSP emulator is available for the Sony PSP and has also been ported to the iPhone and iPod touch.
